summary: An Ordinance repealing Ordinance No. 6493, entitled "An Ordinance providing for the improvement of Battery Street, in the City of Seattle, from the west margin of Fifth Avenue to the east margin of Western Avenue, by planking the same, and providing for the payment therefor by the mode of "Immediate Payment", under the provisions of Ordinance number 5693 of said city, approved December 6, 1899."
